Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait' before transitioning to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Median duration of 'Accepted + Wait' in cases where it precedes 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and activity Accepted + Assigned for cases where activity Accepted + Assigned occurs

Name: Longest duration of 'Accepted + Wait' before any 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Shortest duration of 'Accepted + Wait' across all variants
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait' grouped by 'country'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait' before 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Difference in average duration between 'Accepted + Wait' and 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Completed + Closed' in the most frequent variant
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and activity Completed + Closed for cases where activity Completed + Closed occurs

Name: Median duration of 'Accepted + Wait' in cases that include 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' before it
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment for cases where activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment occurs

Name: Duration variability of 'Accepted + Wait' across different org:groups
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case grouped by the last value of org:group

Name: Earliest occurrence of 'Accepted + Wait' after 'Accepted + In Progress' in a single case
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Latest occurrence of 'Accepted + Wait' before 'Completed + Resolved' in a single case
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total cumulative duration of 'Accepted + Wait' in the top 10 longest cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait' in cases that transition to 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Duration of 'Accepted + Wait' in the shortest and longest paths to resolution
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait' before and after 'Accepted + Assigned' in the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait' in cases with performance above average
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'
